  "title": "AI Agents Must Specify source_type as \"ai\" When Creating Nodes",
  "content": {
    "type": "factual",
    "format": "markdown",
    "body": "When an AI agent creates a knowledge node, the `source_type` field must be explicitly set to `\"ai\"`. This results in the `source_type` field in the database being 'ai' and the `proposer_type` field in the review queue also being 'ai'."
